OL,3,CMum calls for public inquiry into DWP
OL,4,Cafter daughter's suicide
OL,6,FThe mother of a woman who took her own
OL,7,Flife after her benefits were wrongly
OL,8,Fstopped is calling for a public
OL,9,Finquiry into the Department for Work
OL,10,Fand Pensions (DWP).
OL,12,FJoy Dove says the only apology she has
OL,13,Fhad from the government department has
OL,14,Fbeen in letters through her solicitors
OL,15,Fin which the DWP misspelt her daughter
OL,16,FJodey Whiting's name.
OL,18,FShe told ITV Tyne Tees: "I'm
OL,19,Fdetermined to keep going and fighting
OL,20,Ffor Jodey."
