OL,3,CMum calls for public inquiry into DWP
OL,4,Cafter daughter's suicide
OL,6,FMs Whiting, who was housebound and
OL,7,Fdied in 2017, had failed to attend a
OL,8,Fwork capability meeting with the
OL,9,Fgovernment department and was
OL,10,Fsuffering with pneumonia as well as a
OL,11,Fcyst on the brain.
OL,13,FHer mother went to the High Court to
OL,14,Fsecure a second inquest into her
OL,15,Fdeath. That was held in June and the
OL,16,Fcoroner found a move by the DWP to
OL,17,Fstop her benefits was a trigger in the
OL,18,F42-year-old's decision to end her life.
