OL,3,CMum calls for public inquiry into DWP
OL,4,Cafter daughter's suicide
OL,6,FMs Dove is now hoping for access to an
OL,7,FInternal Process Review which she
OL,8,Fbelieves was carried out by the DWP
OL,9,Finto how they handled her daughter's
OL,10,Fcase.
OL,12,FSo far she has been refused this but
OL,13,Fhopes support from other campaigners
OL,14,Fwill compel the DWP to provide her
OL,15,Fwith the review.
OL,17,FThis high profile case has also led
OL,18,Fother people to contact Ms Dove and
OL,19,Fclaim that their case was wrongly
OL,20,Fhandled by the department.
