OL,3,CMum calls for public inquiry into DWP
OL,4,Cafter daughter's suicide
OL,6,FMs Dove is now calling for a public
OL,7,Finquiry into the running of the DWP
OL,8,Fand to hold individual staff connected
OL,9,Fto her daughter's case to account.
OL,11,FIn response to Ms Dove's claims, a
OL,12,Fspokesperson for the Department for
OL,13,FWork and Pensions said: "We continue
OL,14,Fto offer our sincerest condolences to
OL,15,FJodey Whiting's family and are deeply
OL,16,Fapologetic for the misspelling of her
OL,17,Fname.
